    "text": "5.1 Baselines We compare AgenticSZZ against seven SZZ variants and one LLM-based approach, adopting the same baselines as LLM4SZZ [ 36 ] to enable direct comparison. Since we use identical datasets and evaluation methodology, we report baseline results from this prior work where available. 1",
